hopobject.body: Can I take your number? viagra 25 mg or 50 mg Earlier, another White House official, speaking onconditions of anonymity, said Obama was willing to look at aproposal by congressional Republicans to extend the debt ceilingfor six weeks, but insisted that lawmakers also end the 10-daygovernment shutdown. The official said the plan was presented byHouse of Representatives Speaker John Boehner to fellow HouseRepublicans ahead of a meeting with Obama.
